{
  "texts": [
    "First, it contributes to the cohesion of the essay.",
    "By adhering to the PEEL format, each paragraph becomes a self-contained unit of thought, which enhances the essay's overall unity.",
    "Second, employing this structured approach inherently leads the reader through the essay, facilitating a logical flow from one point to the next.",
    "This enhances the ease of comprehending and engaging with the presented argument.",
    "Third, the use of the PEEL structure promotes a level of critical engagement, a quality frequently expected in academic/scientific writing."
  ]
}